/font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23480.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> EQ2.. Why would I WANT to switch? I worked for my stuff...</span><hr size=1> The news of EQ2 is disturbing.. After all this time spent earning the stuff I have and establishing the relations I have and hours of lifetime wasted playing EQ, now EQ is going to go kaput.  There will be no more improvements for EQ after EQ2, the player base will drop dramatically, and everything I've worked for will be gone.  DOH!<br>
