<br>
Then you will enjoy any other game. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulordmaxwell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LordMaxwell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/26/02 4:44:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23480.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: mistake</span><hr size=1> Taronus, did you think EQ was going to be around forever? Did you still think that after they closed the last Meridian 59 server?<br>
